               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-300-cd1532" type="crimeDate">31st of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-300-off1531 t18300916-300-cd1532"></join>, 1 watch, value 3l.; 1 seal, value 7s.; 1 key, value 3s., and 1 pair of overalls, value 7s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-300-victim2461" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Allen
                  <interp inst="t18300916-300-victim2461" type="surname" value="Allen"></interp>
