                     <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2462" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, of Marylebone. I have a silver watch pawned, in the name of Green - I did not take it in; I have a pair of trousers and a jacket, pawned by a groom, but it was not the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-300-person2463">
                  RICHARD 
                  HARTLEY WALL
               <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2463" type="surname" value="HARTLEY WALL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2463" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2463" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I apprehended the prisoner. He told Allen he would show him where the duplicates were - he took us to a green-shop, where we found the one for the watch, and the other at another place, which he directed me to.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-300-person2464">
                  THOMAS 
                  KNIGHT
               <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2464" type="surname" value="KNIGHT"></interp>
