                     <interp inst="t18300916-300-person2464" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a coffee-house keeper. I lent the prisoner 5s. on this duplicate the morning he was apprehended.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He gave me leave to pawn the watch.</p>
